title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2010 SP2 VL x86 en-US November 2015
description:
*****************************************************
Microsoft Office ProPlus 2010 SP2 VL x86 en-US November 2015 
***************************************************--

Supported OS: Windows Vista with SP1, Windows Server 2008, Windows 7, Windows Server 2003, Windows XP.

Release Info

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Version: 14.0.7162.5000
- Format: DAA (ISO compressed)
- Includes all updates published till February 9, 2016

Installation

- Unzip ProPlus14.x64.SP2.en-US-2016.02
- If you know how to handle DAA files, just go ahead
- If you don't: run the batch file Makeiso (this will convert the DAA file to ISO and delete intermediary files)
- Mount or burn ISO file and install Office
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (in add-ins folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)

Bonus (Add-ins folder)

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85
- Office Tab v9.81

Please don't be selfish, seed for a while ...
Thanks !
